snippet.title: Judgement Silversword (Normal Mode 1CC - Normal Ship)
snippet.description: Playing Judgement Silversword's PC release. Personal best. I'm a bit rusty on the true final boss and die to a few silly attacks because I forgot how to dodge them, but this was the first time I ever managed to dodge the Last Judgement attack, so I was happy about that.
